quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Ha, Mim."
  44,2,"Nditsuba khushitabu shinoosinjia."
  44,3,"Toto efwe khwashishia mushilo shietsikhabi, toto efwe khuli abekanyilisi."
  44,4,"Toto eshilo esho buli likhuwa eliamachesi linoosibungwa."
  44,5,"Likhuwa lirula khwifwe, toto efwe nefwe Abaruma."
  44,6,"Tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto Ye ni Omuwulili po, Omumanyi muno."
  44,7,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, nende bioosi bili hakari wabio, toto nimuli mbu mwasuubila noobwatoto."
  44,8,"Abulaho Nyasaye wundi halali Ye tawe, alamusinjia ne afwisinjia. Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi khandi owabasenywe beyimbeli."
  44,9,"Halali bo bali mutsinganakani, babayanga sa."
  44,10,"Kho linda inyanga yelikulu liakharusie omwosi kulolekha."
  44,11,"Kulifunikha Abandu, shino ni eshinyasio eshilulu."
  44,12,"""Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khuyiniliekhwo eshinyasio, toto efwe khulasuubila."""
  44,13,"Okhwitsulila khwabu khubakhoonya shina bulano, ne toto Omurumwa Omwinoosia yamala okhubeetsela."
  44,14,"Mana nibamuhelesia omukongo, nibaboola mbu: “Uno yechesibwa, naye ni Omulalu.”"
  44,15,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhuyiniaho eshinyasio hatiti, ne toto enywe mulakalukha shinga mwali."
  44,16,"Inyanga yakhulikhupa eshikhupo eshikhongo, toto efwe khulibarunga imongo."
  44,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakholela Abandu ba Firauni amatemo imbeli wabu, ne yaboolela Omurumwa woluyali."
  44,18,"Naboola mbu: “Mumbe (akeekhoyeshele), Abasumba ba Nyasaye, toto esie endi Omurumwa omwisikwa khwinywe."
  44,19,"Ne mulakholela Nyasaye obufuru tawe. Toto esie ndalabarerera ebifune biyela."
  44,20,"Ne esie ndiliinda khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi khandi Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi mulandasa amachina tawe."
  44,21,"Ne nimulasuubila tawe, be ehale ninasi.”"
  44,22,"Nasaba Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Toto bano ni Abandu abamabii.”"
  44,23,"Mana Nyasaye naboola mbu: “Rula nende Abasumba banje eshilo. Toto enywe mulalondwakhwo."
  44,24,"Ne oleshe inyanza endio ngayilekhaane. Toto abo ni omukanda kweliyie kwitsa okhusishibwa.”"
  44,25,"Ne balekha emikunda chinga nende tsisebele?"
  44,26,"Nende emimela nende obwami bwoluyali."
  44,27,"Nende obwokholo bwabasangalilanga."
  44,28,"Endio nilwa kali, mana nikhuhelesia ako Abandu bandi."
  44,29,"Ne likulu nohomba eshialo shibialila khulwa bo tawe, ne shibahebwa ebise tawe."
  44,30,"Ne toto khwahabina Abana ba Israili okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiokhubatutuyia."
  44,31,"Okhurulana nende Firauni, toto ye yali Omufuru mubalia babura eshichelo."
  44,32,"Ne toto khwabalobola khumachesi kefu, okhushila ebilonje bindi bioosi."
  44,33,"Ne nikhubahelesia ebimanyisio biefu, amatemo kalolekha."
  44,34,"Toto bano baboolanga mbu:"
  44,35,"“Khubulaho okhufwa khundi tawe halali okhufwa khweimbeli sa, ne efwe shikhulilamusibwa tawe."
  44,36,"Mana lamusiekhwo basefwe nikali mbu muboolanga habwene.”"
  44,37,"Koo, abo naabalayi muno nohomba Abandu ba Tuba’ nende balia baliho imbeli wabu bakhwasishia? Toto abo bali abamabii."
  44,38,"Ne efwe shikhwaloonga likulu nende bioosi bilimwo khumubayo tawe."
  44,39,"Shikhwabiloonga tawe halali khubwatoto, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  44,40,"Toto inyanga yokhubusia eshina ni ebise biabu biabarererwaho boosi."
  44,41,"Inyanga yomwitsa omukhoonyi shalikhoonya owashie nende shiosishiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe."
  44,42,"Halali ulia owa Nyasaye alihelesia tsimbabaasi. Toto ye niwa Amaani, Owobukoosia muno."
  44,43,"Toto omusaala kwa Zaqum."
  44,44,"Ni eshiakhulia shia owetsimbi."
  44,45,"Shinga amafura kasalulusibwe karabachilanga munda."
  44,46,"Shinga okhurabachila khwa amatsi kayile pa."
  44,47,"Baliboolelwa mbu: “Mumutile mana mumusukune hakari womulilo kwa Jahim."
  44,48,"Mana muyombole khumurwe kukwe eshinyasio shia amaatsi karabachilanga."
  44,49,"Pila.. toto (mbu newe welolanga), newe Omwami, Woluyali?"
  44,50,"Toto kano niko kamwakanakanangakhwo.'”"
  44,51,"Toto abaria Nyasaye baliba habundu womulembe."
  44,52,"Mumikunda chomwikulu nende mutsisebele."
  44,53,"Balifwala tsingubo tsinderere tsinyangu tsia hariri..nende tsisiro .. nibahengana."
  44,54,"Endio nilwo lwakaliba, ne khulibabashila mahurul-ain (abakhana bomwikulu)."
  44,55,"Bali laangamwo ebiamo bietsimbia tsioosi nibekhaale nomulembe."
  44,56,"Omo shibalipilamwo lifwa tawe, halali okhufwa khwokhuranga. Ne Nyasaye alibalinda okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Jahim."
  44,57,"Tsino nitsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  44,58,"Ne efwe khwaikhola (Ikurani) okhuba inyangu khululimi lulwo kho banyoole okhwitsulila."
  44,59,"Kho liinda, bosi toto baliindanga butswa."
